body:
OK, I've added a new method `TagSet#onNewTag(Consumer<Tag> customizer)` to support this customization.

E.g. to allow all custom tags to be self-closing:

```java
Parser parser = Parser.htmlParser();
parser.tagSet().onNewTag(tag -> {
    if (!tag.isKnownTag())
        tag.set(Tag.SelfClose);
});

Document doc = Jsoup.parse(html, parser);
```

@tballison @wiedsche please take a pass (using a snapshot build; `mvn install`) and LMK how you go.
